WEBVTT

00:08.607 --> 00:11.608
This week on "VICE":
We see firsthand the results

00:11.693 --> 00:15.312
of Saudi Arabia's ongoing
air campaign in Yemen.

00:23.989 --> 00:26.623
Everything has been
hit and burnt,

00:26.709 --> 00:29.326
every single shop.

00:29.411 --> 00:33.497
And then, the ongoing battle
for LGBT rights in America.

00:33.582 --> 00:36.216
Can you understand how
a gay couple coming in here

00:36.335 --> 00:37.968
would feel
discriminated against?

00:38.053 --> 00:41.472
Americans have the right to
live according to their faith.

00:41.557 --> 00:44.975
This is our time
to take America back.

